{"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkpdfconfiguration"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]},{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkpdfconfiguration"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":"(SBSDKPDFConfiguration) "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKPDFConfiguration"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"pageSize","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is ","type":"text"},{"code":"CUSTOM","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":":","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in this case ","type":"text"},{"code":"dpi","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is used as the conversion ratio to calculate both the physical page and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"image sizes in inches from the bitmap dimensions. ","type":"text"},{"code":"resamplingMethod","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is ignored.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pageSize"},{"type":"text","text":" is not "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CUSTOM"},{"type":"text","text":" AND "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pageFit"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NONE"},{"type":"text","text":":"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in this case "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"dpi"},{"type":"text","text":" is used as the conversion ratio to calculate only the physical image"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"size in inches from the bitmap dimensions. The image is centered onto the page."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"resamplingMethod"},{"type":"text","text":" is ignored."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pageSize"},{"type":"text","text":" is not "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CUSTOM"},{"type":"text","text":" AND "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pageFit"},{"type":"text","text":" is not "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NONE"},{"type":"text","text":":"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in this case the page has a pre-determined physical size and we want to stretch the image to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"fit the page in one of the ways described by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pageFit"},{"type":"text","text":". The image DPI is automatically"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calculated for each image from the given physical page size, page fit setting and image"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"dimensions. There are two sub-cases to consider:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a. "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"resamplingMethod"},{"type":"text","text":" is NONE OR the calculated DPI is less than or equal to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"dpi"},{"type":"text","text":":"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in this case the image is added to the PDF without resampling, which means that the image"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"rectangle is simply rescaled to fit into the page as specified by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pageFit"},{"type":"text","text":" and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pageSize"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"b. "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"resamplingMethod"},{"type":"text","text":" is not NONE AND the calculated DPI is greater than "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"dpi"},{"type":"text","text":":"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in this case the bitmap of the image is resampled to match "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"dpi"},{"type":"text","text":" using the selected method"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"before adding it to the PDF. This will result in a bitmap that is smaller than the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"original image and hence, the resulting PDF will be smaller in size."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The parameters "},{"code":"pageSize","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"pageFit","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"dpi","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"resamplingMethod","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" interact in a complex way"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when adding bitmap images (JPEG, PNG, or raw) to the PDF."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"There are three cases to consider:"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKPDFConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SBSDKPDFConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"ScanbotSDK"}],"roleHeading":"Class","symbolKind":"class","externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKPDFConfiguration","role":"symbol","title":"SBSDKPDFConfiguration"},"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"inheritsFrom","title":"Inherits From","identifiers":["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/objc(cs)NSObject"],"kind":"relationships"},{"type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/objc(pl)NSCopying","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/objc(pl)NSObject","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/s7CVarArgP","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/s28CustomDebugStringConvertibleP","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/s23CustomStringConvertibleP","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/Se","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/SE","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/SQ","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/SH"],"kind":"relationships"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/docume